        Dyad            Monad
+       plus            flip
-       minus           negate
*       times           first
%       divide          reciprocal
&       min/and         where
|       max/or          reverse
<       less            upgrade
>       more            downgrade
=       equal           group
^       power           shape
!       mod/rotate      enumerate
~       match           not
,       join            enlist
#       take/reshape    count
_       drop/cut        floor
$       form/format     format
?       find/invert     unique  invert-guess
@       at              atom    m-amend d-amend
.       dot             value   m-amend d-amend
 
f[x]    is f .,x        is f@x  is f x
f[x;y]  is f .(x;y)
